room_title: Escape room "Antidote" by Escapology Huntsville in Huntsville
room_address: 930 Old Monrovia Rd NW, Suite A, Huntsville AL 35806
room_description: Your research group was invited to gather evidence in Dr. Brandt's lab. He has been working for the enemy to develop a deadly virus that could eliminate thousands of people. Locked in his lab, you have one hour to save your lives and the entire world from destructive chemical warfare. The clock is ticking!
